By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 7
  Paragraph: 16
Title: Fit For Emperors And Kings
---
The next day the two came to see Hu Tzu again, and when they had left
the room, the shaman said to Lieh Tzu, "It certainly was lucky that
your master met me! He's going to get better - he has all the signs of
life! I could see the stirring of what had been closed off!"
